title: LA.Sugar.S01E01.WS.DSR.x264.NY2
description: Chronicling the lives of Los Angeles bakers who cater to upscale clients. Included: Duff Goldman has only three days to create a special birthday cake for Joey Fatone; Jackie Sorkin designs an edible sculpture for a 7-year-old who loves sparkles and butterflies; and sisters Rachel Crystal and Kassandra Workman prepare custom cupcakes for a red-carpet event. Also: vegan desserts for a fund-raiser hosted by Alison Eastwood.
